title: Bugs Bunny : Lost in Time
description:
That wascally wabbit has somehow gotten lost in time, and has to contend with all sorts of obstacles to get back home. Bugs must collect golden carrots in order to obtain the clocks he needs to get back. A fun game for the family, probably better for arcade-experienced players.
